# Secrets and credentials
*.pem
*.key
*.crt
*.p12
*.pfx
*.jks
*.keystore
*credentials*
*kubeconfig*
*secret*.yaml
*secret*.yml
*secret*.json
!*secret*-store*.yaml
!*secret*-store*.yml
# Committed shape-only templates (placeholders, never real keys) — the *secret*.yaml
# rule above otherwise swallows them. Real filled copies drop the `.example` and stay
# ignored. Mirrors the org's `!.env.example` convention.
!*.secret.example.yaml
!*.secret.example.yml

# IAM roles / sensitive AWS config
*role-trust-policy*.json
*assume-role*.json

